{"tid":272133,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣老豆係熱流體力學專家","createTime":"2017-06-05T15:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T02:37:05.000Z","uid":75139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"311b3f794286c16822b32aeb57d066c4e8cefa5e","tid":272133,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"一到夏天就好多偉論<br />\n幾十歲都唔識冷氣係點<br />\n以前第一次買冷氣個陣<br />\n買左返屋企 未裝 擺左係廳張凳上面<br />\n跟住佢想開<br />\n我梗係制止佢<br />\n佢竟然話&quot;好撚熱 開黎涼一陣都好&quot;<br />\n屌 但係個陣係擺係廳中間<br />\n開左一陣 好正常咁一邊噴冷氣一邊噴熱氣<br />\n但熱氣點都多d <br />\n愈來愈熱 佢先知自己柒左<br />\n<br />\n都用過幾年<br />\n佢都仲係覺得，房入面開冷氣，然後開門，會吹到廳都涼埋一份<br />\n但係個廳本身開揚，空氣好流通，又開哂窗其他門又冇關，<br />\n唔知佢個腦點諗野"},{"pid":"311d2cbac3747cd68614b0999867558ebb924739","tid":272133,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"買冷氣之前幾年<br />\n夏天會無端端拎桶水拖地<br />\n話咁樣會涼d<br />\n拖個陣又求9其 整濕地下就算，搞到地下仲污漕 <br />\n同埋拖完有少少水氣，濕度高左仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地板就涼左，氣溫就冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a769bedf05cf4f65bdc5ba3e5fa48a4f5206a92","tid":272133,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"你老豆買左部carnot refrigerator<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9646de125a6a07786180ef1217d8aacb4d255007","tid":272133,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆買左部carnot refrigerator<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700744e8623db3ebe5bc963047d0320e79bf1939","tid":272133,"uid":19929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:55:06.000Z","m