n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都用過幾年<br />\n佢都仲係覺得，房入面開冷氣，然後開門，會吹到廳都涼埋一份<br />\n但係個廳本身開揚，空氣好流通，又開哂窗其他門又冇關，<br />\n唔知佢個腦點諗野</span></blockquote><br />\n想慳電費 開少部 又想涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但唔關窗門就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbfe257184f0fbdba89f3457634b9ddc7a64c11","tid":272133,"uid":66291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:20:11.000Z","msg":"仲有大匹慳電過細匹理論<br />\n爭在冇提名佢去拎諾貝爾獎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83d2417d63fca9fc5a0a37ea6d4cd50c63d5b40","tid":272133,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一到夏天就好多偉論<br />\n幾十歲都唔識冷氣係點<br />\n以前第一次買冷氣個陣<br />\n買左返屋企 未裝 擺左係廳張凳上面<br />\n跟住佢想開<br />\n我梗係制止佢<br />\n佢竟然話&quot;好撚熱 開黎涼一陣都好&quot;<br />\n屌 但係個陣係擺係廳中間<br />\n開左一陣 好正常咁一邊噴冷氣一邊噴熱氣<br />\n但熱氣點都多d <br />\n愈來愈熱 佢先知自己柒左<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都用過幾年<br />\n佢都仲係覺得，房入面開冷氣，然後開門，會吹到廳都涼埋一份<br />\n但係個廳本身開揚，空氣好流通，又開哂窗其他門又冇關，<br />\n唔知佢個腦點諗野</span></blockquote><br />\n想慳電費 開少部 又想涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但唔關窗門就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為廳長期開窗同埋比較開揚冇裝冷氣"},{"pid":"127da5d200cd8294b20d66d99bf6a64bb8fcdda2","tid":272133,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買唔包安裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師傅未到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係送貨同安裝唔同時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9837a6634d2cd9fc486b2a7698cda7fa64d27eb","tid":272133,"uid":36750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:52:40.000Z","ms